title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should be displayed in the data set dialog
description: The output parameter is not currently being displayed in the data set dialog while in the query result page.
OB: On the query result page, there is no data returned.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce this issue:
1. Go to the query result page.
2. Verify that no data is returned.
3. Open the data set dialog and confirm that the output parameter is not displayed.
